IBGE Municipalities — Dataset
==============================

SOURCE
------
Authority: IBGE (Instituto Brasileiro de Geografia e Estatística)
Repository: github.com/kelvins/municipios-brasileiros (CC0 / public domain)
Original data: IBGE official shapefile / municipality registry
License: CC0 1.0 — may be reproduced without restriction

CURRENT FILES
-------------
ibge_municipios.csv — 5571 Brazilian municipalities (all states + DF)
  - Derived from kelvins/municipios-brasileiros CSV (lat/lng from the repository)
  - UF abbreviation mapped from codigo_uf (IBGE state code → two-letter code)
  - Static reference file; never mutated by pipeline
  - Updated when IBGE revises the municipality registry (rare; municipal mergers)

CSV SCHEMA
----------
ibge_code  string    7-digit IBGE municipality code (e.g. "3550308" for São Paulo)
nome       string    Official IBGE municipality name (UTF-8, with diacritics)
uf         string    2-letter state abbreviation (e.g. "SP", "BA", "RJ")
lat        float     Latitude (decimal degrees, negative = south)
lng        float     Longitude (decimal degrees, negative = west)

LOADER BEHAVIOR
---------------
Loaded by brave.lanes.tripadvisor.ibge.load_ibge_csv(path: Path).
- Called once at TripAdvisorDestinosIngest / TripAdvisorAtrativosIngest construction.
- Returns list[IbgeMunicipio] held in memory for the duration of the sweep.
- No per-request file I/O (T-11-02-03).

Resolver: brave.lanes.tripadvisor.ibge.resolve_municipio()
- rapidfuzz token_sort_ratio ≥ 88 (configurable via BRAVE_TA_IBGE_MATCH_THRESHOLD)
- Haversine fallback < 15km (configurable via BRAVE_TA_IBGE_MAX_DISTANCE_KM)
- Returns None on miss → caller quarantines as "ibge_unmatched" (TA-03)

COVERAGE
--------
5571 rows covering all 26 states + Distrito Federal.
Fernando de Noronha (PE) included under Pernambuco.
